name: Punk Trooper
description:
Hes fed up with your shit and he's gonna let you know it! The Punk Trooper has arrived for you displeasure. 

Rebel forces are pissing him off, the empire can be such a drag sometimes and hes sick of it all! Hes always been a misfit and been cast aside like hes got badbrains. His hair smells rancid after a long week and he has made a final stand to raise his black flag. This Punk Trooper is leather clad and ready to roll. 

Colors and imperfections will vary.

name: STORMIE
description:
A long time ago, in a galaxy far, far away...

It is a period of civil war. Rebel
Homies, striking from a hidden
base, have won their first victory
against the evil M.u.s.c.l.e Empire.

During the battle, Rebel Homie spies managed
to steal secret plans to the M.u.s.c.l.e Empire's
ultimate weapon, the Low Rider, an
armored Gas station with enough Hydraulics to destroy an entire planet.

-Brian Bonanno

All figures are hand cast, there may be imperfections and differences in color.

name: IG-666 V1.0
description:
In a time really fucking far away on the place we call home, an IG droid's ship was sucked into a time warp and puked out onto earth, the year 2666. Upon crash landing, the IG droids former body was destroyed, with parts from his dismembered co-pilot he was able to fabricate a human shell. IG-666 was created, in a new terrifying land with magnificent and shitty creatures; IG-666 finds himself battling beasts of demonic proportion. Humanities last hope lies in his wretched hands.


Each cast in a different color, all made to disappoint.

name: Bid Daddy Vain and his Goons.
description:
From a garbage pile far far away comes this horrible troop of decent economic action toy heroes! They were born in the fire, raised in space and live for war, o yea and you can't forget death. 

Each figure is hand cast and may have imperfections.

Please note: figures are made to order, therefore some products might take longer to ship, THAT MEANS THEIR MADE JUST FOR YOU!
